// Tutorial 6 — Velocity (dynamics)
//
// [vel:N] sets the volume/intensity (0-127).
// It applies to all notes that follow until the next [vel].
//
// Try: change the values and listen to the difference.

@core
@controls
@alphabet.western:browser

S -> Soft Loud Soft

Soft -> [vel:40]C4 E4 G4 E4
Loud -> [vel:110]F4 A4 C5 A4
